v0.26.04
Added more volume control logic.
Moved the volume control logic to an addon 'mute'.
Expanded Config Saving functionality and fixed some related bugs.
Added more scrolling input icons, and redid many.
roms now match on parent names, most rom versions should just work with their parent.
E.g. sfiii4fs and sfiii4n are now recognised by the training mode.

Taking the first step to many changes to internal code to hopefully make it more approachable for other developers.

